cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >
  If you reference or build upon this repository, please cite it using the
  metadata below. This project is a proposed proof framework and manuscript
  under review; please cite it accordingly.
title: "A Balance Functional Approach to the Riemann Hypothesis"
abstract: >
  Repository containing manuscript materials, documentation, and support code
  for a proposed balance-functional framework related to the Riemann
  Hypothesis, centered on Phi(s)=Gamma(s)(1-s)zeta(s). The materials are
  organized for mathematical audit and mark unresolved bridges explicitly.
type: software
authors:
